items.name: Picnic-Adventure-Game-In-JAVA
items.description: Yogi Bear is on a mission to collect all the picnic baskets in Yellowstone National Park, but obstacles and rangers stand in his way! The park contains mountains and trees that act as obstacles, and rangers who move horizontally or vertically. If a ranger gets too close (one unit distance), Yogi loses a life.
